Package: atspR
Title: Automated Time-Series Preprocessing in R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Data", "Scientist", email = "ds@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An automated preprocessing framework for time-series data providing tools 
    for missing value analysis, imputation (linear interpolation & KNN), 
    temporal train/test splitting, feature scaling (Min-Max, Z-score, Robust), 
    and k-fold cross-validation. Designed for time-series and tabular datasets 
    with a clean, composable API and rich visual diagnostics.
